{"tid":1415983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【8.5罷工集會】警隊裝甲車出動　朝天水圍方向進發　隨時候命","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:53:13.000Z","uid":282925,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"52ec33f556093646624ee0d5bf74c1d52a5518aa","tid":1415983,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"政府修訂《逃犯條例》激發市民持續兩個月上街抗議，今日多區爆發激烈衝突，據《香港01》了解，警隊裝甲車「銳武」已由粉嶺基動部隊基地，向天水圍方向出發，並隨時候命。翻查資料，警察機動部隊（PTU）於2009年耗資3,600萬元，購入6部「銳武」（Unimog U5000）防彈裝甲車，並一併引入了兩部只可接駁於裝甲車使用、俗稱「聲波炮」的長距離揚聲裝置。<br />\n<br />\n「銳武」是警隊使用的第三代裝甲車，它具備上一代「剎臣」所有功能；連司機可載10人；全車防彈；無任何武器，需要時依靠車上人員的裝備。"},{"pid":"9e8a549db711c3777d21f5a0c0a33f0a9fce7cc9","tid":1415983,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"From 香港01"},{"pid":"842ca1f43894dd1671b69a7c6ac0281ab65e8722","tid":1415983,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea62cf1cdad2533c1dab6a074820fa43db9d250","tid":1415983,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690f7bfc1276faa6941c457fb341994a6d4b5fd2","tid":1415983,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960bfe79a1590296995afadd492852f0662747e6","tid":1415983,"uid":290530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":